[[ᱚᱱᱩᱥᱠᱟ ᱥᱚᱨᱢᱟ]] ᱫᱚ ᱩᱛᱛᱚᱨᱯᱨᱚᱫᱮᱥ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱟᱭᱚᱫᱷᱭᱟ ᱨᱮ ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱞᱮᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref>{{cite news|title=Anushka Sharma celebrates 25th birthday in Goa|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/tabloid/anushka-sharma-celebrates-25th-birthday-in-goa/article1-1053171.aspx|work=Hindustan Times|date=1 May 2013|accessdate=10 March 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130503020831/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/Anushka-Sharma-celebrates-25th-birthday-in-Goa/Article1-1053171.aspx|archivedate=3 May 2013}}</ref><ref name="Anushka-UP">{{cite web|last=Gupta |first=Priya (18 December 2012) |title=There is no system in the film industry: Anushka |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/There-is-no-system-in-the-film-industry-Anushka/articleshow/17649937.cms? |work=The Times of India |accessdate=10 March 2014 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121217213847/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/There-is-no-system-in-the-film-industry-Anushka/articleshow/17649937.cms |archivedate=17 December 2012 |df= }}</ref> ᱟᱡᱤᱡᱡ ᱟᱯᱟᱛ ᱫᱚ '''ᱠᱚᱨᱱᱮᱞ ᱚᱡᱚᱭ ᱠᱩᱢᱟᱨ ᱥᱚᱨᱢᱟ''' ᱢᱤᱫ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱯᱷᱟᱹᱫᱽ ᱟᱹᱢᱟᱹᱞᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱟᱨ ᱮᱸᱜᱟᱛ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱜᱷᱟᱨᱚᱡᱽ ᱥᱚᱦᱮᱫ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾<ref name="Anushka-UP"/><ref>{{cite web|last=Joshi |first=Sonali (8 April 2012) |title=Anushka Sharma buys three flats worth Rs.10 crore in Mumbai's posh area |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/anushka-sharma-buys-property-worth-rs.-10-crore-in-mumbai/1/183488.html |work=India Today |accessdate=10 March 2014 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311014951/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/anushka-sharma-buys-property-worth-rs.-10-crore-in-mumbai/1/183488.html |archivedate=11 March 2014 |df= }}</ref> ᱟᱯᱟᱛ ᱫᱚ ᱩᱛᱛᱚᱨᱯᱨᱚᱫᱮᱥ ᱨᱮ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱱᱤᱡ ᱟᱨ ᱮᱜᱟᱛ ᱫᱚ ᱜᱚᱨᱚᱵᱟᱞᱤ ᱨᱤᱱᱤᱡ ᱾<ref>{{cite news|last=Singh|first=Mauli (29 December 2010)|title=Ranveer is my favourite co-star: Anushka|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news-interviews/ranveer-is-my-favourite-co-star-anushka/articleshow/7183257.cms|work=The Times of India|accessdate=10 March 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Bahadur |first=Sona (4 April 2011) |title=Cloud Nine |url=http://www.verveonline.com/96/people/anushka.shtml |work=Verve |accessdate=10 March 2014 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310124540/http://www.verveonline.com/96/people/anushka.shtml |archivedate=10 March 2014 |df= }}</ref> ᱟᱡᱤᱡ ᱢᱟᱨᱟᱝ ᱫᱟᱫᱟ ᱚᱱᱩᱥᱠᱟ ᱥᱟᱶ ᱢᱮᱥᱟ ᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱛᱮᱭᱟᱨ ᱮ ᱮᱦᱚᱵ ᱞᱮᱫ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ, ᱩᱱᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱞᱟᱦᱟ ᱛᱮ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱱᱟᱹᱭ-ᱯᱷᱟᱹᱫᱽ (Navy) ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱠᱟᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref name="watt">{{cite news|last=Kumar |first=Sunaina |title=The 1,000 watt girl |url=http://archive.tehelka.com/story_main49.asp?filename=hub090411ANUSHKA_SHARMA.asp |date=9 April 2011 |accessdate=10 April 2011 |work=Tehelka |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220205406/http://archive.tehelka.com/story_main49.asp?filename=hub090411ANUSHKA_SHARMA.asp |archivedate=20 December 2013 |df= }}</ref>

ᱚᱱᱩᱥᱠᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱠᱟᱹᱴᱤᱡ ᱵᱮᱲᱟ ᱨᱮᱜᱮ ᱵᱟᱝᱜᱟᱞᱚᱨ ᱛᱮ ᱥᱮᱱ ᱞᱮᱱᱟᱭ, ᱚᱸᱰᱮᱮ ᱤᱫᱟᱹᱨ ᱵᱮᱲᱟ ᱠᱷᱮᱸᱰᱟᱣ ᱞᱮᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾ ᱵᱟᱝᱜᱟᱞᱚᱨ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱯᱷᱟᱹᱫᱽ ᱟᱥᱲᱟ ᱨᱮ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱯᱟᱲᱦᱟᱣ ᱮᱦᱚᱵ ᱞᱮᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱟᱨ ᱵᱟᱝᱜᱟᱞᱚᱨ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ''ᱢᱟᱶᱴ ᱠᱟᱨᱢᱮᱞ ᱢᱟᱦᱟᱵᱤᱨᱫᱟᱹᱟᱲ'' ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱦᱩᱱᱟᱹᱨ (Arts) ᱨᱮ ᱥᱚᱱᱮᱨ ᱮ ᱥᱤᱫ ᱞᱮᱫ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref name="facts">{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/specials/hall-of-fame/photo-features/Anushka-Sharma-Lesser-known-facts/photostory/45178001.cms |title=Anushka Sharma: Lesser known facts |work=The Times of India |accessdate=2 June 2015 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621071452/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/specials/hall-of-fame/photo-features/Anushka-Sharma-Lesser-known-facts/photostory/45178001.cms |archivedate=21 June 2015 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-just-how-educated-are-bollywood-heroines/20120118.htm#8 |title=Just how educated are bollywood heroines |publisher=Rediff.com |date=18 January 2012 |accessdate=2 June 2015 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130805134000/http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-just-how-educated-are-bollywood-heroines/20120118.htm |archivedate= 5 August 2013 |df= }}</ref> ᱩᱱᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱚᱰᱮᱞᱝ ᱟᱨ ᱰᱚᱚᱨᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱦᱩᱭᱩ ᱥᱟᱱᱟ ᱞᱮᱫᱮᱭᱟ, ᱢᱮᱱᱠᱷᱟᱱ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱷᱮᱞᱚᱸᱰᱟᱭ ᱢᱮᱱᱛᱮ ᱫᱚ ᱵᱟᱭ ᱟᱥᱟ ᱞᱮᱫ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾ <ref name="facts"/> ᱚᱱᱩᱥᱠᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱥᱚᱱᱮᱨ ᱥᱤᱫ ᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱢᱚᱰᱮᱞᱤᱝ ᱞᱟᱹᱤᱫ [[ᱢᱩᱢᱵᱟᱭ]] ᱛᱮ ᱥᱮᱱ ᱞᱮᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref name="tribune">{{cite news|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/851478/10-facts-about-anushka-sharma-you-didnt-know/ |title=10 facts about Anushka Sharma you didn't know |work=The Express Tribune |date=11 March 2015 |accessdate=6 June 2015 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522105528/http://tribune.com.pk/story/851478/10-facts-about-anushka-sharma-you-didnt-know/ |archivedate=22 May 2015 |df= }}</ref> ᱤᱞᱟᱭᱤᱴ ᱢᱮᱱᱮᱡᱽᱢᱮᱱᱴ ᱨᱮ ᱚᱱᱩᱥᱠᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱯᱨᱚᱥᱟᱫᱽ ᱵᱤᱫᱽᱯᱟ ᱛᱟᱨᱤ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱠᱟᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾ <ref name="Koimoi biography">{{cite web|url=http://www.koimoi.com/actress/anushka-sharma/ |title=Anushka Sharma's Biography |publisher=Koimoi |accessdate=6 June 2015 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150611153214/http://www.koimoi.com/actress/anushka-sharma/ |archivedate=11 June 2015 |df= }}</ref> ᱒᱐᱐᱗ ᱥᱟᱹᱦᱤᱛ ᱨᱮ  ᱚᱱᱩᱥᱠᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱞᱟᱠᱢᱮ ᱯᱷᱮᱥᱚᱱ ᱩᱭᱤᱠ ᱨᱮ ᱣᱮᱱᱰᱮᱞ ᱨᱚᱰᱨᱤᱠᱥ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱞᱮᱫ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱛᱟᱭᱚᱢ ᱥᱚᱱᱥᱤᱞ, ᱣᱤᱥᱯᱚᱨ, ᱱᱟᱛᱷᱮᱞᱞᱟ ᱡᱩᱣᱮᱞᱟᱨᱥ ᱟᱨ ᱯᱷᱤᱭᱟᱛ ᱯᱷᱚᱞᱤᱭᱚ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱮ ᱮᱰᱵᱷᱮᱴᱟᱡᱽ ᱞᱮᱫ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref name="Koimoi biography"/>
